    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">This tab is</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> on the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Farms_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Water Balance Subregions</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box.</text></para>
